    "A clear rationale always helps to increase the understandability and trustworthiness of a system in users' eyes.",
    "Along with rationale, if end users are given explanations, they can identify instances in which the AI system has made errors or generated decisions that deviate from the desired conclusion.",
    "This information can help the developers to enhance the AI model.",
    "Providing explanations enables end users to acquire knowledge and understanding by gaining insights into the AI system's decision-making process.",
    "Using this tool can enhance users' educational experiences and facilitate the development of informed decision-making skills for future endeavors."
  ],
